### Visit API

### Get all visits (paginated)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/visits?page=0&size=20

### Get visit by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/visits/{{visitId}}

### Create visit
POST {{host}}/api/v1/visits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petId": "{{petId}}",
  "vetId": "{{vetId}}",
  "diagnosis": "Routine checkup",
  "treatment": "Vaccination",
  "notes": "Pet is healthy",
  "cost": 50000
}

### Update visit
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/visits/{{visitId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "diagnosis": "Minor skin infection",
  "treatment": "Antibiotics prescribed",
  "notes": "Follow-up in 2 weeks",
  "cost": 75000
}

### Process payment for visit
POST {{host}}/api/v1/visits/{{visitId}}/payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50000
}
